<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='849000' id='t-849000'>But I hope that you are at least partly convinced</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='852000' id='t-852000'>that it is not impossible to build a brain.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='855000' id='t-855000'>We can do it within 10 years,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='857000' id='t-857000'>and if we do succeed,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='859000' id='t-859000'>we will send to TED, in 10 years,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='861000' id='t-861000'>a hologram to talk to you. Thank you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='864000' id='t-864000'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
